<br>
IMO - religion is the organization and standardization of beliefs into a belief system.  It is made to be a &quot;color-by-number&quot; way for people to understand the concept of God (or &quot;gods&quot; depending upon the belief) and his meaning to the world and a person without having to truly delve into one's own personal thought processes.<br>
<br>
